its for the metal-rich globular\nclusters and tangentially-biased orbits for the metal-poor globular clusters,\nwhich remains a puzzling finding for an accretion-dominated halo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Dec 2017 18:10:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
