es a generalized coercivity result by exploring properties of\nthe enriching operators and using the discrete spectrum estimate in its $C^1$\nconforming relative finite element space, which can be obtained by using the\nspectrum estimate of the Cahn-Hilliard operator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Dec 2017 20:28:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 22:40:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 22:22:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 15 Sep 2018 21:23:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
