e the current bounds on $\\Delta(\\Delta m^2_{31})$ by at least one\norder of magnitude. We also study the sensitivity to the other oscillation\nparameters. Finally we show that, if CPT is violated in nature, combining\nneutrino with antineutrino data in oscillation analysis will produce imposter\nsolutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 15:43:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 08:49:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-06"}
